  "ineq-properties": {
    "title": "不等式基本性质",
    "exercises": [
      {
        "id": "ineq-prop-1",
        "unitId": "ineq-properties",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "choice",
        "prompt": "(多选)下列结论正确的是\nA.若$a>b$，则$ac> bc$\nB.若$a>b>0$，则$\\dfrac{1}{a}<\\dfrac{1}{b}$\nC.若$ac^2>bc^2$，则$a>b$\nD.若$a<b$，则$a^2<b^2$",
        "options": [
          "A",
          "B",
          "C",
          "D"
        ],
        "answer": "BC",
        "gaokaoConnection": "不等式基本性质：注意乘法时$c$的符号，倒数在正数范围内成立"
      },
      {
        "id": "ineq-prop-2",
        "unitId": "ineq-properties",
        "difficulty": 1,
        "type": "choice",
        "prompt": "若$a,b,c\\in \\mathbf{R}$，$a>b$，则下列不等式成立的是\nA.$\\dfrac{1}{a}<\\dfrac{1}{b}$\nB.$a^2>b^2$\nC.$a|c|>b|c|$\nD.$\\dfrac{a}{c^2+1}>\\dfrac{b}{c^2+1}$",
        "options": [
          "A",
          "B",
          "C",
          "D"
        ],
        "answer": "D",
        "gaokaoConnection": "$c^2+1>0$恒成立，不等式两边同除正数不等号方向不变"
      },
      {
        "id": "ineq-prop-3",
        "unitId": "ineq-properties",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "choice",
        "prompt": "(多选)已知$a,b,c,d$均为实数，则下列命题正确的是\nA.若$a>b,c>d$，则$a-d>b-c$\nB.若$a>b,c>d$，则$ac> bd$\nC.若$a>b,c>d>0$，则$\\dfrac{a}{d}>\\dfrac{b}{c}$\nD.若$ab>0,bc-ad>0$，则$\\dfrac{c}{a}>\\dfrac{d}{b}$",
        "options": [
          "A",
          "B",
          "C",
          "D"
        ],
        "answer": "AD",
        "gaokaoConnection": "不等式性质的综合运用，注意正负号对乘除的影响"
      },
      {
        "id": "ineq-prop-4",
        "unitId": "ineq-properties",
        "difficulty": 2,
        "type": "choice",
        "prompt": "(多选)已知实数$a, b, c$满足$a>b>c$，且$a+b+c=0$，则下列说法正确的是\nA.$\\dfrac{1}{a-c}>\\dfrac{1}{b-c}$\nB.$a-c>2b$\nC.$a^2>b^2$\nD.$ab+ bc>0$",
        "options": [
          "A",
          "B",
          "C",
          "D"
        ],
        "answer": "BC",
        "gaokaoConnection": "由$a+b+c=0$且$a>b>c$可推出$a>0,c<0$，结合条件分析各选项"
      }
    ]
  },
